data.description: Less than 3 miles to downtown Hendersonville, this beautifully updated home sits on almost an acre of prime Kanuga Rd. property with mature trees and flat grassy areas. Inside you'll find an inviting living space with a gas fireplace. Step down into your beautiful kitchen with high ceilings. Two bedrooms on the main level and the large third bedroom on the lower level. The basement offers a spacious laundry room and great extra spaces for an office or craft room! Don't miss your opportunity to live with no HOA in an ideal Hendersonville location. We noticed some deterioration on the edge of the septic riser lid. Quote to repair is attached ($267).
